          <title>
            <string language="en">Frequency of musical instruments  pan pipes</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Frequenz der musikalischen Instrumentwanne Rohre</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Fréquence des pipes musicales de casserole 
d'instruments</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Freqüência das tubulações musicais da bandeja
dos instrumentos</string>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Frequenza dei tubi musicali della vaschetta degli

            <string language="x-mt-el">Συχνότητα των μουσικών παν σωλήνων οργάνων</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Frecuencia de los tubos musicales de la cacerola 
de los instrumentos</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">Third of four illustrations on matching the pan pipes to their corresponding sound frequency. Shown here is the frequency corresponding to the longest pipe.</string>
          </description>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Third von vier Abbildungen auf dem 
Zusammenbringen der Wanne leitet zu ihrer entsprechenden stichhaltigen
Frequenz. Hier gezeigt die Frequenz, die dem längsten Rohr 
entspricht.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Le tiers de quatre illustrations sur apparier la 
casserole siffle à leur fréquence saine correspondante. 
Montrée ici est la fréquence correspondant dans la plus longue
pipe.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">O third de quatro ilustrações em combinar a 
bandeja conduz a sua freqüência sadia correspondente. É 
mostrada aqui a freqüência que corresponde à tubulação a mais 
longa.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Un terzo di quattro illustrazioni sul abbinare la
vaschetta convoglia alla loro frequenza sana corrispondente. È 
indicata qui la frequenza che corrisponde al tubo più lungo.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Τρίτο τεσσάρων απεικονίσεων στο ταίριασμα των παν 
σωλήνων την αντίστοιχη υγιή συχνότητά τους. Εμφανισμένη 
εδώ είναι η συχνότητα που αντιστοιχεί στο μακρύτερο σωλήνα.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">El tercero de cuatro ilustraciones en 
corresponder con la cacerola transmite a su frecuencia sana 
correspondiente. Se muestra aquí la frecuencia que corresponde 
al tubo más largo.</string>
          </description>
